p.d: Private delivers top talent from France, England, Hungary and Russia to three horse hung horny guys looking for action on the beaches of Ibiza. These stallions have a plan, a milionaire's villa and a way with words. All they need is an opportunity. Featuring Sharon Lee and Mira Sunset as a fierce Franco Hungarian duo as well as Henessy, Jasmine Jae, Kristall Rush and Amy Wild "Sun Oil Sluts" is a perfect cure for a rainy day.
